37
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,750
What do you mean? We don't have anything.

38
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:21,750
All of our tools and materials are back home.

39
00:03:21,750 --> 00:03:23,750
All right everyone. Empty your pockets.

40
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:25,750
Let's see what we've got to work with.

